	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "An officer, probably a Legate, who led the forces of Cassius against Rhodes (App. BC 4.72). Perhaps to be identified with the conspirator against Augustus, Fannius Caepio (RE no. 16; see I. de Delos 4.1.1623 -Choix 169)." .
